Package: AdjacencyScore
Type: Package
Title: Computes a bivariate metric to rank pairs of features by how colocalized they are in a graph
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kiya W.", "Govek", email = "govekk@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package calculates f((e^{kA}-I)/k)g for each pair of features f and g on a graph with adjacency matrix A and constant k between 0 and 1.
Imports: 
  igraph,
  MASS,
  Matrix,
  parallel,
  RANN
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
